description.en: Floki Elon has learned a few tricks and lessons from his meme father, Doge Coin. A new crypto birthed by fans & members of the Doge Coin online community. Floki Elon seeks to impress his father by showing his new improved transaction speeds & adorableness. He is Hyper-deflationary with an integrated smart staking system built in to reward you, so more Floki Elon coins are being automatically added to your wallet each transaction. Simply Love, pet, and watch your Floki Elon grow.
